\v 18 Nansi inhlakanipho\x + 17.9.\x*. Olokuqedisisa kabale inombolo yesilo\x + 15.2.\x*; ngoba iyinombolo yomuntu\x + 21.17. 7.9.\x*, lenombolo yaso ingamakhulu ayisithupha lamatshumi ayisithupha lesithupha.